gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 100, Trail Blazers 92
gameRecap.excerpt: Golden State defeats Portland, 100-92. For Golden State, Stephen Curry led the way with 22 points (five 3PM), seven rebounds, and eight assists while aided by Jonathan Kuminga (19 points, six rebounds) in the victory. Deandre Ayton finished with 25 points, 11 rebounds, and three steals while Scoot Henderson recorded 18 points and 12 assists for Portland in the losing effort. Golden State improves to 45-35, while Portland moves to 21-59 in the loss.
